{"tid":1848534,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"有無人出個型D既膠大水樽DIY防疫頭盔設計?","createTime":"2020-01-28T13:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T18:47:49.000Z","uid":169195,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"30f952392b20d9d691f3d59a24552d8302529890","tid":1848534,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/b9ZaQ2F.jpg\" /><br />\n幅相大家都見過好7<br />\n<br />\n但係比起口罩<br />\n好處: 唔會焗面, 照計可以更氣密(視乎頸位點整), 個外露位遠離個口鼻所以替換時更安全, 唔會蒸眼鏡, 擋埋眼, 膠易清潔可reuse, 材料易入手.....<br />\n<br />\n缺點: 視野問題可能搵隻平面D既樽會好D, 7既問題就靠DIY高手設計..."},{"pid":"261c7105ed9d6f2f186e08d0d0e5379c6db71ed5","tid":1848534,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:35:17.000Z","msg":"你自己整個出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f60213e255147524d1824a31b8ada3f3b6cb3b6","tid":1848534,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當年</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RaUgNwQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRaUgNwQ.png&h=6d2974dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加入英蝗後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39HFuLj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39HFuLj.png&h=1e072a70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f95d0ff545cddda74220167d2f4bce15907097b2","tid":1848534,"uid":172349,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mWNvRHi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmWNvRHi.jpg&h=c2aaca27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84c0e864ea893d48924546487735ab057c20d5e3","tid":1848534,"uid":894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f95d0ff545cddda74220167d2f4bce15907097b2","tid":1848534,"uid":172349,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mWNvRHi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmWNvRHi.jpg&h=c2aaca27&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9c4738004218d6188bacc027639a947506d28e","tid":1848534,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=ada0c097\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護目鏡</span>：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a></span></span> / <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=97386a25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\nVPN 大踢爆：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D112386483628876%26id%3D112357283631796%26__tn__%3D%252As-R&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=6fdfdb9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳，避免沉底<br />\n<br />\n最近口罩同N95 都賣曬，部分手足屋企口罩已經就黎用盡，今日同大家介紹下可以防沙士+TG嘅濾罐同濾棉。第一，係for 用曬/買唔到口罩嘅手足，第二係希望方便大家一次過買齊發夢+出街嘅裝備，就算沙士完左，自用送禮都可以繼續名貴大方。<br />\n<br />\nN95/R95/P95 口罩基本上係particulate respirator, 外科口罩防嘅係飛沫粒子，即係我地用防毒面具代替，就要裝particulate filter，換言之，就係濾棉！<br />\n<br />\n濾棉最高級別就係P100，防油性+非油性粒子，即係TG（油性）同埋病毒都可以防，型號包括2091, 2097, 2297, 6035（只有英國製）,7093 等等，而60926等等嘅6092X 系列濾罐，因為內置P100 濾棉，所以一樣ok <br />\n其中，6053 同 7093 棉係防水的，清潔消毒會較方便，而60926表面亦有膠盒。<br />\n<br />\n有強國人做過測試，係北京霧霾毒氣之下，3M 2091 用左十一日過濾能力都係跌左1%，手足請自行考慮幾耐換一次。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon 大log買亦有便，大家可以組團買。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com.au%2F3M%2Fen_AU%2Fcompany-au%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B8711017%2B3294471754%26rt%3Drud&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=32441d79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com%2F3M%2Fen_US%2Fcompany-us%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B3294776429%26rt%3Drud&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=2d7385f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<br />\n2003 年沙士，淘大嘅清理人員就係用2091棉+600X 罐（罐理論上唔洗，應該係防佢地嘅清潔同消毒藥水）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">如何清潔防毒面具可參考依段片，有教disinfection，主要都係漂白水同消毒劑<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdE5IweYn3T4&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=afae233f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n清潔步驟：<br />\n入到屋企唔好除裝備住，用酒精紙巾抹左面具同濾棉/罐表面先，跟住抹埋手再洗手（點解又要酒精又要洗手係有原因的），跟住就除面罩，再跟番片入面嘅教學清潔<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n防毒面具方面，建議大家買/用6800 或者其他包曬成塊面嘅款式，咁樣就唔洗帶眼罩，一舊野保護曬成塊面，最安全。因為你戴半面+眼罩，咁就多舊野清潔，同埋部分眼罩封唔曬，冇咁安全。<br />\n<br />\n型號方面，全面嘅建議大家買6800，順便擋埋橡膠子彈，半面嘅就買7502/ 6500，兩款手足都表示舒適度幾高。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112044766987392%2Fposts%2F119490526242816%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=ea36d99c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n</a><br />\n酒精搓手液 vs 洗手梘液</span>"},{"pid":"d3ef5661ee9e641ebcd37064416e0775f68fdfd8","tid":1848534,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:48:47.000Z","msg":"圖中有戴埋口罩架"},{"pid":"6178fc8d3f163ba80f778b3a5cd660f8478b77f6","tid":1848534,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3ef5661ee9e641ebcd37064416e0775f68fdfd8","tid":1848534,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:48:47.000Z","msg":"圖中有戴埋口罩架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"咁DIY版頸位攪得好咪唔駛MASK"},{"pid":"8e5bab2e738