e=\"color: blue;\">街市超市</span></strong><br />\n呢類必去嘅地方一定要提防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭盔式嘅防疫防具，一般都係唔會密封<br />\n記住<br />\n最大功能都係用嚟<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">防飛抹真接接觸到頭部<br />\n即我地嘅五官</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/9PgvV8ale90lQwfQTZ/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F9PgvV8ale90lQwfQTZ%2Fgiphy.gif&h=96ac47f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起細細個有買個類似嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">太陽帽</span></strong><br />\n以21世紀嘅日用品嚟講<br />\n呢樣係最唔誇張、平民容易買得到嘅防具<br />\n大家不坊搵下屋企有無<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbnail.image.rakuten.co.jp/@0_mall/naturenature/cabinet/main01/acty2851and2801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbnail.image.rakuten.co.jp%2F%400_mall%2Fnaturenature%2Fcabinet%2Fmain01%2Facty2851and2801.jpg&h=3a63b4fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2dcan0armyq93.cloudfront.net/photo/odai/600/e074cc348b8543fff62cc9b0d7e7b5a4_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2dcan0armyq93.cloudfront.net%2Fphoto%2Fodai%2F600%2Fe074cc348b8543fff62cc9b0d7e7b5a4_600.jpg&h=7d85bcbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">購買途徑應該有好多，不詳例</div></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好覺得街上有人用係好奇怪<br />\n日本人平常都會用嚟擋太陽擋雨<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dk4duPwUYAAVNr_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDk4duPwUYAAVNr_.jpg&h=a5acf7cc&s={SIZE}\" />"}}